91302,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"[革命成功]香港人已經階段式勝利中 和理非同文宣組可以退場休息下 依家只要等美國出手就贏<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491379</a>"},{"pid":"3d89ff8f8f536d336e4842df13d864004f9a40fd","tid":1491302,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef8481eed7e148fe2e69020fd0509a6c6a14d92","tid":1491302,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}